{"tid":1633671,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[全世界入] 由今日起 只有手足 沒有派系","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:24.000Z","uid":172599,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d96b33066512fc2c0d066f3a986486701023a98","tid":1633671,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"眼見大家成日話勇武點點點，和理非又點點點<br />\n<br />\n咁樣只會慢慢係意識上將大家分為兩組人，而咁樣係會分裂落去<br />\n<br />\n因此，今日開始，大家只以手足 相稱<br />\n<br />\n沒有勇武派或和理非<br />\n<br />\n依d係行動既分類，例如，今日既活動係和理性質，或今日既活動係勇武性質<br />\n<br />\n以後行動一出，大家只有手足<br />\n<br />\n而檢討既時候，大家變左唔會批評大家，而係&ldquo;我覺得今日既勇武活動點點點...我覺得個和理活動可以點點點&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n從而不會兩批人對罵，自傷感情<br />\n<br />\n因爲大家其實一直目標一致，一直都係手足！"},{"pid":"9a3e8ecf587eddc15bbfb18ceedfc91b7a489286","tid":1633671,"uid":120604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"01a30db0b97559875a6c0a51d74ab01ae6ce7f1f","tid":1633671,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推<br />\n手足加油</span>"},{"pid":"afe2c0f3983738d8955becb2bb1243cb82b17eac","tid":1633671,"uid":210752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75dfb837f72a9625f1caea15aaf2a2e02a211bf2","tid":1633671,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"只爆黨鐵"},{"pid":"551d8e9bf677a2c1d78b402d5cc129b1ad93bbd3","tid":1633671,"uid":210752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b98394691ac7e531f990edcc4d17ef4cddcc86a","tid":1633671,"uid":210752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"876f13f3266fab18370f1286e2ea2971a9b664fe","tid":1633671,"uid":240664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0